Giving your consent:

To comply with General Data Protection Regulations (GDPR), by signing this registration form it confirms your consent for the following:

•	Inclusion of your name on FPFL related league standings and match reports published on the FPFL website and associated social media including the FPFL ‘What’s App’ group(s).

•	To be contacted via email, ‘What’s App’, text messaging or phone call as appropriate with regards to FPFL related updates such as cancellations, change of venue/time/date, league standings & match reports.

•	Filming/photography by the FPFL and any related publishing of said filming/photography on the FPFL website and associated social media. Prior notice will always be given in advance if this does take place.

You may change your consent by notifying the FPFL at any time in the future in writing.
